title: Behind the Scenes: NYX FACE AWARDS TOP 30 2013 - Unboxing Beauty Haul
description:
A BIG THANK YOU TO NYX COSMETICS for allowing me the chance to showcase my make up! It's been an amazing experience!! Also would love to thank the sponsors, BIG SEXY HAIR and LULUS for giving me amazing hair products and clothes!

VOTE FOR ME! If you like me and want to be friends ^.^ haha
http://www.nyxfaceawards.com for BABAMITSANNE!!!

Thank you to my AMAZING friends for helping me make this amazing video!
Especially Phuong and Christopher! You guys are the bomb!
Thank you Jayson for letting me take over and film at SATAY Bistro Restaurant!
Thank you to Columban and Adam for featuring in my video as sexy musicians!
Thank you to Josh and Hai for helping me as well! You guys are awesome!
